<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Mod id="521b8777-0977-4859-a5ee-3e411a732e5c" version="2.1">
  <Properties>
    <Name>LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_NAME</Name>
    <Description>LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_DESCRIPTION</Description>
    <Teaser>LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_TEASER</Teaser>
    <Authors>LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_AUTHORS</Authors>
    <Homepage>https://space.bilibili.com/385456816</Homepage>
    <SpecialThanks>LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_THANKS</SpecialThanks>
    <AffectsSavedGames>1</AffectsSavedGames>
    <SupportsMultiplayer>0</SupportsMultiplayer>
    <SupportsHotSeat>0</SupportsHotSeat>
    <CompatibleVersions>1.2,2.0</CompatibleVersions>
  </Properties>

  <!-- 模组文本 -->
  <LocalizedText>
    <Text id="LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_NAME">
      <en_US>[COLOR_Civ6LightBlue]Harmony in Diversity v2.1: Civ6 Plus[ENDCOLOR]</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>[COLOR_Civ6LightBlue]【和而不同 v2.1】文明6 Plus[ENDCOLOR]</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>
    <Text id="LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_TEASER">
      <en_US>Create a brand new Civ6. Current Version v2.1.</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>创造一个全新的文明6。当前版本为v2.1。</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>
    <Text id="LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_DESCRIPTION">
      <en_US>Civ6 Plus: Harmony in Diversity 2.1. Building on the spirit of diversity from Harmony in Diversity I, this expansion introduces a wealth of new mechanics, technologies, cultures, and Great People—crafted to deliver distinct playstyles and civilizations, offering passionate Civilization VI players a thoroughly refreshed experience. [NEWLINE]Current version is v2.1.</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>文明6 Plus: 和而不同2.1。继承了和而不同1代百花齐放的精神，新增了大量新机制、科技、文化和伟人，意图打造丰富而各具特色的玩法和文明，为热爱文明6的友好玩家们带来全新的游戏体验。当前版本为v2.1。 [NEWLINE][NEWLINE]特别鸣谢1代制作组：DeepLogic, 小灰灰, 小小雨10101, 六亿神州尽舜尧, 傲娇的红莉栖, 利牙菠萝, 陈又, YT, wltk, 黑毛毛小魔仙, 柚子, Winged Hussar, o(╯□╰)o, 咸鱼喵, 笑笑, 时代的先驱, 五年, wlhxzwa, 阿伟, 榖音, 奥伊米亚, 凯欧利, 音痴痴c, 戴胜, Blood_Moon, Kekeya, 话心, 亚瑟, Yogomove, 美菲拉斯, xubwa, 镜花水月, 小河, 法拉墨, Vearmus, lp, Siv, 流浪de蒲公英</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>
    <Text id="LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_AUTHORS">
      <en_US>Xhh, C, Wei, Apry, Siv, Fox</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>小灰灰丶不吃羊、六亿神州尽舜尧、阿伟、小学、Siv、酸酸酸酸酸狐狸</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>
    <Text id="LOC_HARMONY_IN_DIVERSITY_THANKS">
      <en_US>Hemmelfort for his MOD tutorial on BiliBili.[NEWLINE]Burger's Lettuce for English Text Improvement.[NEWLINE]JNR, Leugi, Ithildin, Phantagonist for Assets editing tutorial.[NEWLINE]Xianqu and Arthur for laying the foundation of this project.</en_US>
      <zh_Hans_CN>感谢Hemmelfort在Bilibili发布的模组教程。[NEWLINE]感谢Burger's Lettuce的英文翻译优化。[NEWLINE]感谢JNR、 Leugi、 Ithildin、 Phantagonist等开发者对制作组提供的模型支持和教学。[NEWLINE]感谢时代的先驱和亚瑟为和而不同2.0起到的的奠基作用。</zh_Hans_CN>
    </Text>
  </LocalizedText>

